OL,5, The Pensions Regulator is investigating
OL,6, whether the owner of one of the UK's   
OL,7, oldest social enterprises fraudulently 
OL,8, failed to make disabled workers'       
OL,9, pension contributions.                 
OL,11,FThe 168-year-old soap maker Clarity was
OL,12,Fbought from administration in 2020.    
OL,14,FWorkers say they lost their jobs and   
OL,15,Fare still owed redundancy payments,    
OL,16,Ffurlough money and wages.              
OL,18,FThe owner, Nicholas Marks said he      
OL,19,Flooked forward to "clarifying the      
OL,20,Fposition" with the Regulator.          
